{"tid":2110918,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"武漢地鐵施工毀家園，維權女慘遭斷手筋仍相信中共：共產黨的天下，不會放任那些基層官員胡作非為，坑害百姓的！","createTime":"2020-07-16T08:25:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T10:20:35.000Z","uid":1886,"like":8,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0cd9ebc8cf04064a5118a43e01303f2d306e6394","tid":2110918,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T08:25:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.video.appledaily.com/china/20200716/WYZBI4RUPOWXAYUWOXFMRNKXWI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.video.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200716%2FWYZBI4RUPOWXAYUWOXFMRNKXWI%2F&d=CgM6%2BPDcwTI4Uk%2BisK9n39UqyFx8t7fe88%2BQEXu6%2F%2FM%3D&h=85d7ff53\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.video.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200716%2FWYZBI4RUPOWXAYUWOXFMRNKXWI%2F&h=2778993d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.video.appledaily.com/china/20200716/WYZBI4RUPOWXAYUWOXFMRNKXWI/</a><br />\n<br />\n去年10月9日，她獨自一人到長江委社區協商「地鐵施工致房屋受損無法居住」，要求作出賠償，但當局竟然派出多人圍毆她，令她的左臂斷了幾條筋脈，手術費就要4萬至10萬元（4.4萬至11萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n姚青的左臂被扯傷後，連拿餸菜的力氣也沒有，傷勢令她不能出差，被迫辭去一份到全國做諮詢培訓、年收入20萬元（約22萬港元）以上的穩定工作，要靠老母親2,800元（約3,100港元）的退休金過活。她連月來到武漢地鐵集團、勞動街社區、武漢市信訪局等多個部門奔走，但維權道路十分艱辛，但她並未言棄：「只要還有一絲希望，我就不會放棄追求公平和正義，而我仍然堅信，共產黨的天下，不會放任那些基層官員胡作非為，坑害百姓的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！」"},{"pid":"e5a2380ceeeb34c8cf88998a8b4289e50170cf0d","tid":2110918,"uid":35457,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T08:26:20.000Z","msg":"真係命賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6d581eeb5070dac03c1e0f2b2c25e61696460db","tid":2110918,"uid":155095,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T08:26:43.000Z","msg":"皇帝陛下英明神武<br />\n<br />\n只是官員欺壓百姓<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54d0925d7490a3446597f686c7cab4352a068559","tid":2110918,"uid":48362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T08:27:12.000Z","msg":